item.title: CVE-2017-2105|2024-08-05T13:39:32.279Z -- presentcast%20inc. -- tver%20app%20for%20android
item.description: The TVer App for Android 3.2.7 and earlier does not verify X.509 certificates from SSL servers, which allows man-in-the-middle attackers to spoof servers and obtain sensitive information via a crafted certificate.
